본 file 은 disease-axis-orthogonal roadmap. hexa-bio 의 5 axis 가 bone marrow failure (조혈모세포 부전 — aplastic anemia + MDS + AML) 에 어떻게 기여하는지 cross-axis mapping + 신규 약물 기준 falsifier inventory.

(Distinct from `.roadmap.disease_hematology` — hematology 는 응고/항응고 FXa apixaban 중심; 본 entry 는 조혈모세포 quantitative + qualitative deficit 중심. 2017-2024 첫 FDA approval 폭발: midostaurin 2017 / venetoclax 2018 / gilteritinib 2018 / luspatercept 2019 / 2020 ivosidenib 1L AML / 2024 quizartinib 1L AML / 2024 imetelstat first telomerase MDS.)

scope:
- aplastic anemia (acquired + inherited Fanconi)
- 골수형성이상증후군 (MDS — IPSS-R risk-stratified)
- 급성 골수성 백혈병 (AML — molecular subtype-driven)
- 급성 림프구성 백혈병 (ALL — Ph+ + Ph-like + CD19 CAR-T)
- 만성 골수성 백혈병 (CML — BCR-ABL TKI generation)
- 만성 림프구성 백혈병 (CLL — BTKi + BCL2i)
- 다발성 골수종 (multiple myeloma — IMID + PI + anti-CD38 + BCMA CAR-T + bispecific)
- myelofibrosis (MF — JAK inhibitor)
- 진성적혈구증가증 (PV — ropeginterferon 2021)
- 본태혈소판증가증 (ET)
- paroxysmal nocturnal hemoglobinuria (PNH — eculizumab/ravulizumab/iptacopan/danicopan)
- atypical HUS (ravulizumab + crovalimab 2024)
- thrombotic thrombocytopenic purpura (TTP — caplacizumab 2019)
- inherited bone marrow failure (Fanconi / dyskeratosis congenita / DBA)

