## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **revumenib Revuforj 2024** = first menin inhibitor — KMT2A-rearranged + NPM1-mutated AML. menin-KMT2A interface 가 FDA 첫 승인된 protein-protein interaction 표적 in heme malig. quantum-VQE 의 PPI scaffold 가 직접 fit.
2. **imetelstat Rytelo 2024** = first FDA telomerase inhibitor. LR-MDS transfusion-dependent 적응증. lipid-modified 13-mer oligonucleotide 가 hTR template 결합. quantum-VQE 의 RNA-oligonucleotide 결합 modeling 한정.
3. **asciminib Scemblix 2021** = first allosteric STAMP (Specifically Targeting the ABL Myristoyl Pocket) CML. ATP-competitive CML 6+ 세대 후 next mechanism. quantum-VQE 의 allosteric pocket leverage.
4. **ivosidenib + enasidenib + olutasidenib + revumenib + ropeginterferon 2017-2024** = AML/MDS/PV 임상 paradigm shift (small molecule + targeted disease-modifying). cytotoxic chemo-only era 종료.
5. **CAR-T 5 + bispecific 4 (CD19 + BCMA + GPRC5D + CD20) 2017-2024** = "living drug" + "off-the-shelf" alternation. CRS/ICANS 부작용 + tisa-cel BCMA secondary T-cell malig signal 2024 = long-term safety open.
6. **BCMA CAR-T 4년 차 + GPRC5D bispecific (talquetamab 2023)** = MM 5+ relapse line 임상 상황 변화. BCMA-loss escape resistance + GPRC5D 가 next target.
7. **luspatercept Reblozyl 2019** = TGF-β SMAD2/3 ligand trap → late-stage erythroid maturation 회복. EPO-R-axis 의 alternative. quantum-VQE 의 ActR2B/A 가 sotatercept (cross-pulm PAH) 와 mechanism 동일.
8. **iptacopan + danicopan 2023-2024** = PNH oral C-pathway inhibitor — IV C5 mAb 의 oral alternative. compliance 향상.
9. **eltrombopag aplastic anemia 1L 2018+** = TPO-RA + ATG/CsA 1차치료 paradigm. immunosuppressive 가 disease-modifying 가 아니라 supportive.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, BMF + heme-malig 임상 의미 한정.

